quran[118]{c,v,t}:
  23,1,"GooŇč…óii malaama gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen."
  23,2,"∆Āeen huloo…ďe ka ndeer Juulde ma…ď…ďe ko…ďe yankinii…ďe."
  23,3,"E …ďeen …óurnii…ďe ga rayrayti( bolle mehre)."
  23,4,"E …ďeen ittoo…ďe askal on."
  23,5,"E …ďeen reen…ďe farjuuji ma…ď…ďe …ói."
  23,6,"Si wonaa e dow suddii…ďe ma…ď…ďe ma …ďe √Īaame ma…ď…ďe …óe njeyi(horbe), haray kam…ďe …ďe ngonaa feletee…ďe."
  23,7,"OOn mo …óa…ď…ďi …ďaawo …óum, haray ko …ďeen ngoni jaggitoo…ďe …ďen."
  23,8,"E …ďeen aynu…ďe koolaaje ma…ď…ďe e aadiiji ma…ď…ďe …ói."
  23,9,"E …ďeen …ďe ka√Īun ko…ďe reen…ďe e dow Juulde ma…ď…ďe …óen."
  23,10,"∆Āee [sifor…ďe …óii sifaaji …óoo] ko kam…ďe ngoni ronoo…ďe …ďen."
  23,11,"∆Āeen ronoyat…ďe Firdawsi on kam…ďe ko …ďe duumotoo…ďe e ndeer makko."
  23,12,"GooŇč…óii Min tagii ne…ó…óaŇčke on immorde e lasili loopal."
  23,13,"Refti Min mba…ói mo to…ď…ďere [maniiyu] e ndeer √Īii…ďirde ku…ďindiinde."
  23,14,"Refti Min Tagi to…ď…ďere nde he…ó…óere, Min Tagi he…ó…óere nden huyre, Min Tagi huyre nde ∆īi'e, Min koltini ∆īi'e …óeteewu. Refti Min pu…ó…óanii mo Tagoore woo, barkanii Alla Mo∆ī∆īo Tak…óo."
  23,15,"Refti onon …ďaawo …óuum ko on maayoo…ďe."
  23,16,"Refti pellet, onon √Ďande Darngal on imminoyte."
  23,17,"GooŇč…óii Min Tagii dow moo…óon …óati jee…ói…ói, Min ngonaani kadi welsindii…ďe gaayi tagoore nde."
  23,18,"Min njippini immorde ka kammu ndiyam e emmbere [haaju tagoore nde], Min ndewni …óam ka leydi, pellet, Minen ko Nden Hattan…ďe e dow na…ďugol …óam."
  23,19,"Min pu…ó…óani on sabu majjam gese immorde e tamarooje e inabuuje, no woodani on ndeer ton dim…óe …óuu…óu…óe ko e majje √Īaamoton."
  23,20,"E leggal ngal no yalta immorde to Tuuri Siinaa hangal fu…óina gu∆īam [nebban wujetee…óam] e li'am [maafir…óam] wonan'de √Īaamoo…ďe."
  23,21,"Pellet, no woodani on e neemoraa…ói …ói tasakuyee, Mi…óen njarna on bo…ó…óum e ko woni kon ka deedi majji, no woodani on e majji nafooje keew…óe, ko immorde e majji kadi √Īaamoton."
  23,22,"Ko e hoore-majji e hoore laa…óe …óe ndoonndete…óon."
  23,23,"GooŇč…óii Min Nulii Nuuhu e yim…ďe makko …ďe o maaki : eey mon yo yim…ďe am, ndewee Alla. Dewetee…óo alanaa on ko woori mo. Enee, on kulatah?""."
  23,24,"Hooree…ďe mbatu ngun mbii'ani …ďen yeddu…ďe immorde e yim…ďe makko …ďen: ""Oo wonaani si ko o …ďanndiŇčke yeru mo'on homo faalaa nde o …ďurnotoo e dow moo…óon. Sinndo Alla muuyino O jippinayno Malaa'ikaaji, min naniraani …óum baabiraa…ďe amen aran…ďe …ďen""."
  23,25,"KaŇčko o wonaani si wonaa ko o gorko mo jinna woni e mu'um, habbitee mo tun haa see…óa."
  23,26,"O maaki: ""Joom am, wallam e ko …ďe njennimi kon""."
  23,27,"Min wahayini fa'ade e makko yo o lesu laana kan e dennka amen e Wahayu Amen, si Yamiroore amen nden arii hu…ď…ďinirde nden pullitike [ndiyam] naatu e ndeer makka immorde e kala nooneeji …óin …ói…ói-…ói…ói. E koreeji ma, si wonaa …ďeen konngol ngol aditii e mu'um, wata a haaldu e am fii …ďen too√Īu…ďe, pellet, kam…ďe ko …ďe yooletee…ďe."
  23,28,"Si a fotondirii aan e …ďeen won'…óu…ďe e maa…óa e dow laana kan, haray maaku: ""Yettoore ndeen ko Alla woodani, On danndu…óo Min immorde e yim…ďe too√Īoo…ďe …ďen""."
  23,29,"Maaku: ""Joomam, jippinam e jipporde barkinaande ko Aan woni mo∆ī∆īo Jippinoowo""."
  23,30,"Pellet, no e ndeer …óum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo] sayeeje, haysi men laatike ko min njarribotoo…ďe."
  23,31,"Refti Min 'u…ó…ói …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe yiirde wo…ď…ďe goo."
  23,32,"Min Nulii e ma…ď…ďe Nulaa…óo jeyaa…óo e ma…ď…ďe, …óum woni ndewee Alla, dewatee…óo on ko woori Mo. E on kulatah [Mo]?!""."
  23,33,"Batu e yim…ďe makko …ďen yeddu…ďe …ďe penni kawroygol e Laakara on, Min neemini …ďe ka ngurdam aduna wi*i: ""Oo wonaani si wonaa …ďannduŇčke yeru moo…óon homo √Īaama ko √Īaamoton kon homo yara kadi ko njaroton kon""."
  23,34,"Mi woo…óndii si on …óoftike …ďannduŇčke yeru mo'on, pellet, onon on tuma ko on hayru…ďe(pertube)."
  23,35,"Enee, o 'oton wonan'dema onon si on maayii on laatike mbullaari e ∆īi'e, wonan'dema onon ko on yaltinoytee…ďe?!"
  23,36,"Wo…óndii woori kon ko poda…óon."
  23,37,"[∆Āe mbi'i:] ""∆äum wonaani si wonaa nguurdam amen aduna, mi…óen maaya min nguura kadi, minen min ngnaani immintinoytee…ďe""."
  23,38,"KaŇčko o wonaani si wonaa ko o gorko pekindii…óo fenaande fawi e Alla, minen non, min mgnaami gooŇč…óinat…ďe mo."
  23,39,"O maaki: ""Joom am, wallam e ko …ďe njeddii kam kon""."
  23,40,"O Daali: ""See…óanii tan, Mi woo…óndii …ďe ngontat nimsu…ďe""."
  23,41,"Haacaango ngon nanngi …ďe e Goonga, Min mba…ói …ďe duu√Īo, halkaare wonanii yim…ďe too√Īoo…ďe …ďen."
  23,42,"Refti Min pu…ó…ói …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe gire wo…ď…ďe goo."
  23,43,"Mofte woo lajal majje ngal adotaako …óe, …ďe nee…ďnantake kadi."
  23,44,"Refti Min Nuli Nulaa…ďe amen …ďen ko …ďe jokkondir…ďe, tuma kala ari e mofte Nulaa…óo majje on …ďe njedda mo Min njokkini yoga e ma…ď…ďe yoga, Min mba…ói …ďe yewtereeji, wo…ó…óineede wonanii yim…ďe …ďe gooŇč…óintaa …ďen."
  23,45,"Refti Min Nuli Muusaa e musi…ó…óo makko on Haaruuna wond'ude e aayeeje amen …óen e hujja …ďanngu…óo."
  23,46,"Fa'ade e Fir'awna e mbatu mu'um ngun, …ďe mawnintinii …ďe laatii yim…ďe townitii…ďe."
  23,47,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""Enee, hara min ngooŇč…óinat yim…ďe …ói…óo yeru amen, hara yim…ďe ma…ď…ďe ko maccu…ďe amen?"""
  23,48,"∆Āe njeddi …ďen …ói…óo, …ďe laatii jiyaa…ďe e halkaa…ďe …ďen."
  23,49,"GooŇč…óii Min ngokkiino Muusaa Deftere nde mbelejo'o kam…ďe …ďe peewa."
  23,50,"Min mba…ói ge…óal Mariyama on e neene makko Ma'ande, Min werni …ďe fa'ade e tulde joomiraare √Īi…ďrude e callungol."
  23,51,"Eey mon yo Nulaa…ďe, √Īaamee immorde e laa…ďu…ói …óin ngollon ko mo∆ī∆īi, pellet Min, Mi…óo Anndi ko ngolloton kon."
  23,52,"E pellet, kaa Diina mo'on ko Diina woota, ko Min woni Joomi mo'on lulee Kam."
  23,53,"∆Āe ta∆īi fiyaake ma…ď…ďe on hakkunde ma…ď…ďe dente, kala fedde no farnora ko woni kon ka mayre."
  23,54,"∆äalu …ďe e siwrere nde haa e dummunne."
  23,55,"Enee, hara …ďe cikku wonan'dema ko Min …ďeydiri …ďe kon immorde e jawdi e …ďi…ó…ďe."
  23,56,"Min njaccinana …ďe e mo∆ī∆īereeji, ko woni …ďe tin'aa."
  23,57,"Pellet, …ďern …ďe ka√Īum immorde e kulol Joomi ma…ď…ďe ko …ďe hul…ďe."
  23,58,"E …ďen …ďe ka√Īum ko …ďe gooŇč…óin…ďe sayeeje Joomi ma…ď…ďe …óen."
  23,59,"E …ďeen …ďe ka√Īum …ďe nhonah sirkanoo…ďe Joomi ma…ď…ďe."
  23,60,"E …ďen okkay…ďe ko …ďe ngokkaa kon, hara …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen ko hul…óe [Alla], wonan'dema kam…ďe ko fa'ade ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe …ďe nduttoytoo."
  23,61,"∆Āeen [sifaa…ďe …óii sifaaji …óoo] he…ďe yaccoo e mo∆ī∆īereeji …ói, hara kam…ďe ko …ďe adotoo…ďe e majji."
  23,62,"Min pawaani woŇčkii si wonaa fodde baw…óe makki, no ka amen Deftere wowlaynde Goonga kan, hara kam…ďe …ďe too√Īoytaake."
  23,63,"Ko woni, …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óe no e welsungo immorde e …óum, no woodani …ďe kadi golle ga …óuum ko kam…ďe ngollate …óe."
  23,64,"Haa si Min nanngirii neeminaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen Lepte …óen njaka yoo kam…ďe he…ďe haaca."
  23,65,"Wata on haacu hannde, pellet onon, on wallataake immorde e amen."
  23,66,"GooŇč…óii Aayeeje Amen …óen no janngee e taweede moo…óon, laati…óon ho…óon nduttoo e dow codduli moo…óon."
  23,67,"Ko on mawnintinii…ďe sabu [jeyeede makka] ho…óon kiira haalde bon…ói."
  23,68,"Enee, teskaaki konngol ngol, kaa hara ar e ma…ď…ďe ko araani e baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe adinoo…ďe …ďe?"
  23,69,"Kaa …ďe nganndaani Nulaa…óo ma…ď…ďe on, hara kam…ďe ko …ďe faaytu…ďe mo?"
  23,70,"Kaa hara …ďe mb'ay feetere no e makko? Ko woni, o addanii …ďe Goonga kan …ďur…ďe heewde e ma…ď…ďe ko a√Ī…ďe Goonga kan."
  23,71,"Sinndo Alqur'aana jokkuno belee…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin bonayno e …ďen wonu…ďe e majji, ko woni, Min addanii…ďe waaju ma…ď…ďe ngun, kam…ďe ko…ďe …óurnii…ďe ga waaju ma…ď…ďe ngun."
  23,72,"Kaa a tori …ďe njeenaari? [Awa] ko njeenaari Joomi maa…óa ndin …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude, ko KaŇčko woni Mo∆ī∆īo Arsikoowo."
  23,73,"Pellet, an ha…óa noddude fa'ade e Laawol Pocciingol."
  23,74,"E pellet, …ďen …ďe mgooŇč…óinaani Laakara on ko …ďe selu…ďe e Laawol ngol."
  23,75,"Sinndo Min Yurmino …ďe, Min hunci ko he…ďi …ďe kon immorde e lorra, …ďe duumotono e ndeer bewre ma…ď…ďe he…ďe wemmboo."
  23,76,"GooŇč…óii Min nanngirii …ďe Lepte …óen, …ďe koykinanaaki Joomi ma…ď…ďe …ďe yankinaaki."
  23,77,"Haa si Min ngudditii e dow ma…ď…ďe dammbugal marungal Lepte sa…ótu…óe, e jaka, kam…ďe e nyder …óum ko …ďe ta∆īii …ďe."
  23,78,"Ko KaŇčko woni On u…ó…óan∆äo on nan…óe …óen e gii…óe …óen e …ďer…óe …óen, fan…óii ko njeettoton."
  23,79,"Ko KaŇčko woni On Tak…óo on ka leydi ko fa'ade ka makko moo…ďoyte…óon."
  23,80,"Ko KaŇčko woni on mo no wurna O wara no woodani mo luutindirgol jemma on e √Īalawma on, enee, kaa on hakkiltah?"
  23,81,"Ko woni, …ďe mbii' yeru ko aram…ďe …ďe mb'inoo ko."
  23,82,"∆Āe mb'i: ""Enee, si min maayii min ngonii mbullaari e ∆īi'e, hara minen ko min immintinoytee…ďe?"""
  23,83,"GooŇč…óii min podanooma …óum minen e baabiraa…ďe amen ko adii, …óum wonaani si wonaa tinndi adinoo…ďe."
  23,84,"Maaku: ""Ko hommbo leydi ndi woodani e …ďeen won…ďe e mayri, si tawii hi…óon nganndi?"
  23,85,"Aray …ďe mbi'a: ""Ko Alla woodani"" maaku: ""Enee, on mbaajitotaako?"""
  23,86,"Maaku: ""Ko hommbo woni Jom kammuuji …óin jee…ói…ói e Jom Arsi mawki kin?"""
  23,87,"Aray …ďe mbi'a: ""Ko Alla"" maaku: ""Enee, on kulatah [Alla]?"""
  23,88,"Maaku hommbo woni e Junngo Mu'um Laamu kala hu'unde hara KaŇčko homo walla O walletaake, si tawii on laatike ho…óon nganndi?"
  23,89,"Aray …ďe mbi'a: ""Ko Alla woodani"" maaku: ""Enee, ko honno mbilirte…óon ?"""
  23,90,"Ko woni, Min ngaddanii …ďe Goonga kan, pellet kam…ďe ko …ďe fen…ďe."
  23,91,"Alla jogitaaki …ďi…ó…óo, dewetee…óo laataaki wond'ude e Makko, e jaka [si wa…óum wa…óuno] kala dewetee…óo yaadayno e ko o tagi kon, yoga e ma…ď…ďe townitotono e dow yoga. Senayee wonanii Alla e ga kon ko …ďe cifotoo."
  23,92,"Ganndu…óo ko wirnii kon e ko seedaa ko O Toowii e gai ko …ďe cirkata kon."
  23,93,"Maaku: ""Jooma am si A hollii kam ko …ďe podaa kon""."
  23,94,"Jooma am, wota A wa…óam e yim…ďe too√Īoo…ďe …ďen."
  23,95,"Pellet, Minen fii yo Min holle ko Min fodi …ďe kon ko Min Hattan…ďe […óum]."
  23,96,"Du√Īir nden hu'unde …ďurnde mo∆ī∆īude [hu'unde] bonunde nden, ko Minen nganndi ko …ďe scfoto kon."
  23,97,"Maaku: ""Jooma, mi moolorii ma immorde e kodooje Seytanuuji …ói""."
  23,98,"Mi moolorii ma Jooma am nde …ói tawata kam."
  23,99,"Haa si maayde arii e go…ó…óo e ma…ď…ďe nden, o wi'a: ""Jooma am nduttee kam""."
  23,100,"Mbelejo'o min, mi ngollay ko mo∆ī∆īi e ndeer kon ko mi accunoo, …óum wa…óataa, ngol ko kanngol ko kaŇčko wowli ngol, no hedde …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe heedo haa √Ďande nde …ďe imminoytee."
  23,101,"Si wuttaama ka alaadu, askaaji alah hakkunde ma…ď…ďe nden √Ďande, …ďe lanndandirtah ."
  23,102,"Kala on mo jisti(teddi) manndake (peesirgal)muu…óum, haray ko …ďen …óon ngoni maloytee…ďe …ďen."
  23,103,"Kala mo manndake [mo∆ī∆īi] mu…óum hoytii, (hoyi)haray ko …ďen …óon ngoni hayru…ďe pittaali muu…óum, ko ka ndeer Jahannama woni ko …ďe luttintee."
  23,104,"Yiite ngen no sunna je'ece ma…ď…ďe …óen, hara kam…ďe e ndeer magge ko …ďe √Īir…ďinii…ďe."
  23,105,"Enee, hara Aayeeje Am …óen laataaki no janngee e taweede mo'on, laati…óon ho…óon njedda …óe?"
  23,106,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""Joomi amen, ko malkiso amen ngon foolii min, min laatinoke yim…ďe majju…ďe."""
  23,107,"Joomi amen, yaltin min e magge, si min ruttike hara pellet, minen ko min too√Ī…ďe."
  23,108,"O Daala: ""√Ďii…ďee e ndeer magge wota on kaalanam""."
  23,109,"Pellet, laatinoke fedde e jiyaa…ďe Am …ďen hi…ďe mbi'a: ""Joomi amen, min ngooŇč…óinii haforan men njurme∆äaa men ko Aan …ďuri Mo∆ī∆īude Yurmetee…ďe …ďeen""."
  23,110,"NJogiti…óon …ďe jalnori(jalkigol), haa …ďe njejjintini on jaŇčta Am, laati…óon ho…óon njala …ďe."
  23,111,"Min Mi yo…ďii …ďe hannde sabu ko …ďe mu√Ī√Īinoo kon, pellet, kam…ďe ko kam…ďe ngoni malaa…ďe …ďeen."
  23,112,"O Daali: ""No foti heewde ko √Īii…ď…óon ka leydi, limoore duu…ďi?"""
  23,113,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""Min √Īii…ďii √Īallal maa…óum yoga e √Īallal, lanndo limoo…ďe …ďeen."""
  23,114,"O Daali: ""On √Īii…ďaani si wonaa see…óa, sinndo onon on laatino ho…óon nganndi."""
  23,115,"Enee, on cikku wonan'dema ko Min Tagiri on ko puyndan, hara onon on mduttetaake fa'ade ka Amen?!"
  23,116,"Alla Toowii Laam…óo Goongu…óo On, dewetee- …óo alah si wonaa KaŇčko Jooma Arsi Tedduki kin."
  23,117,"Kala noddu…óo wond'ude e Alla dewetee…óo goo, daliil alanah mo e …óum, anndu pellet, hasboo- re makko ko ka Joomi makko, pellet KaŇčko, O malnatah heefer…ďe …ďeen."
  23,118,"Maaku: ""Jooma am, Yaafo Yurmo ko Aan ∆Āuri Mo∆ī∆īude Yurmetee…ďe …ďen."""
